# Arsenal Match Stats Dashboard 🏟️

This project analyzes Arsenal's 2023/24 Premier League performance using match data from Understat. It visualizes key metrics such as expected goals (xG), goals scored, and overperformance trends. You can also generate match summaries using a local LLM like Mistral via Ollama.

## Features

- 🔎 Fetch real Arsenal match data
- 📊 Visualize xG vs Goals using Matplotlib/Streamlit
- 🧠 (Optional) Generate match summaries with LLMs like Mistral

## Tools Used

- Python (Pandas, Matplotlib)
- Streamlit (for dashboard UI)
- Understat API
- Ollama + Mistral (LLM)

